<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    Jason sleeps a few times with his mistress, Sybil, when he and Victoria were "engaged" and from what I remember he also "visits" and takes Sybil to th<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    Jason sleeps a few times with his mistress, Sybil, when he and Victoria were "engaged" and from what I remember he also "visits" and takes Sybil to the opera while he is in London for a while after he marries Victoria. I do not think you can really call it cheating him sleeping with his mistress while engaged to Victoria as it was a charade. Doing it after they got married is another matter...<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
