              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/42316620-azet?shelf=romance-genre">romance-genre</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/42316620-azet?shelf=my-most-beloved-favourites">my-most-beloved-favourites</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/42316620-azet?shelf=steamy-erotic">steamy-erotic</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/42316620-azet?shelf=charm-comedy-humor">charm-comedy-humor</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/42316620-azet?shelf=jealous-smitten-possessive-hero">jealous-smitten-possessive-hero</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1411528382" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14405759832293688700">&quot;Once and Always&quot; always has,and will always be one of my most favourite romantic novel of all time...!<br/><br/>This is my 11:th time re-reading it and i never get tired.Judith McNaught has a magical spell over the way she writes and the way she flows the epic gesture in her stories.<br/>This book has it all for a romantic lover like myself.It`s amazingly beautiful plot enticed me and excited me and the unique and passionate love-story between the brightful raven-haired beauty Victoria Seaton and the notoriou</span>
  <span id="freeText14405759832293688700" style="display:none">"Once and Always" always has,and will always be one of my most favourite romantic novel of all time...!<br /><br />This is my 11:th time re-reading it and i never get tired.Judith McNaught has a magical spell over the way she writes and the way she flows the epic gesture in her stories.<br />This book has it all for a romantic lover like myself.It`s amazingly beautiful plot enticed me and excited me and the unique and passionate love-story between the brightful raven-haired beauty Victoria Seaton and the notorious and dark-looking Jason Fieldings.Their unhidden desire,overpowering love,the angst...the epic scenes just bewitched me into falling in love with this book forever..<br /><br />Victoria is a heroine i utterly adore and love,and GOSH how i just want to be her friend!She is so charming,funny and brave and her glowing nature and goodness just brighted her beauty for everyone.She is a woman who fights for what she wants and i rooted for her from the start to the end.<br /><br />and then.......<br /><br />We have the undenyable INCREDIBLE arrogant,rawly sexy,darkly passionate tortured brooding hero Jason Fieldings WHO JUST HAVE MY HEART,ALL OF IT!<br /><br />GOSH HOW I LOVE THIS MAN!<br />Jason practically shone throughout the book,every scene,every emotion,thought...everything..EVERYTHING,EVERY LITTLE DETAIL had my attention.He is a dangerous Alpha-hero who only wishes to find peace,home...love.<br />He is one of the most tortured heroes i have ever met,and what he had to go through child-hood,OH GOD HOW HORRIBLE...SO UTTERLY HORRIBLE.<br />He had a beautiful soul who only craved love from Victoria,who he thought she felt for someone else.His destructive pain over her rejection just broke my heart,and through this misunderstanding i just suffered with both of them.His everlasting and craving love for the heroine was too much for me,and the heart-breaking scene later on in the book just made me cry to pieces...<br /><br />It was so epic...so romantic...so beautiful.<br /><br />Jason and Victoria has a chemistry like no other and reading this book was like watching a soap-opera.I enjoyed every word,every page,everything!I LOVE LOVE LOVE this amazing book so much."Once and Always" will always be one of the most unforgettable epic romantic love-story of all time.I want to re-read it all over again now.<br /><br />***<br /><br /> “Because I knew another lass like you long ago. She had your warmth and your courage. She taught me how it feels to trust, to love, and to be loved. I don’t fear dying because I know she’s there, waiting for me. Most men love easily and often, but Jason is more like me. He will love only once—but it will be for always.”</span>
  <a data-text-id="14405759832293688700" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


